name: 'Primordial Paradox'  art poster
description:
'Primordial Paradox' by David Higgins.

This powerful image transforms and transends natural forces and creates male vital energy into sublimnity and action. Maro and microcosoms unite, air, fire, water and earth underpin sex, life and death. 

Size including trim: 92cmx 60cm

Posters are hand signed by David.
